* [[Prayer potion]]s or [[super restore]]s (can replace food with more potions if experienced)
* [[Ring of shadows]] for teleporting back, or [[amulet of the eye]] if [[scarred tablet]] has not been acquired yet
* [[Anglerfish]] are for boosting health before starting a kill to lessen interruptions during the volley of attacks, as well as chip damage from the roar attack
* [[Shadow Rush]] is just as effective as [[Shadow Barrage]] in stunning the boss, whilst costing three times less
* A magic staff with autocast can be used to auto-cast Shadow spells. [[Thammaron's sceptre]] is a lighter weight option. Manually casting a spell is the same number of clicks, with the bonuses of saving an inventory slot and having a bigger click box in the spellbook tab by filtering out spells you lack the runes to cast.
* [[Twisted bow]] can optionally be used for the backside attack, as it usually deals higher damage than crossbow attacks due to the vastly increased minimum hit, especially with a Dizana's quiver so as to not require two inventory slots

